parameters:
\N<Detective>*sigh* With this, the report is finished... Now I
just have to convey the matters to the Board of
Education...

\N<Misaki>\C[24]It must be tough to have work on your
daughter's birthday. I hate being a dad.

\N<≪Wife≫>\C[24]Since I'm out eating with Misaki, please
have the curry in the cupboard for dinner.

\N<≪Wife≫>\C[24]I'm going to bed first, so please don't make
any noise when you come back.

\N<Detective>...So, the paving of the school route is the
responsibility of the administration, not the
school...

\N<???>It's common sense that the responsibility for
managing and supervising the school route lies
with the school, isn't it?

\N<???>Thanks to you, my child got injured! How do you
plan to take responsibility for this?!

\N<???>Ugh, the vice principal dealing with another
idiotic situation? That's just too much.

\N<???>It seems like there have been more of them
lately~. Poor things~.

\N<Detective>...Regarding the response of the guardian who came
this morning, as a general rule, the handling of
the guardian of the assigned student...

\N<???>Oh well, the parents are demanding to speak to
someone higher up. Ah, it's already quitting time
so I'll be leaving now.

\N<???>Vice Principal... We've been receiving complaints
from the parents regarding your handling.

\N<???>The guidance of the teachers is the responsibility
of the vice principal...
\N<Detective>Sigh... What on earth am I supposed to do... Hm?

\N<???>The vice principal seems unreliable, don't you
think~

\N<???>If someone like that is our boss, it really brings
down our morale.

\N<???>He's slow at work too~. He lacks judgment, you
know, judgment skills lol.

\N<Detective>(An unreasonable guardian who doesn't listen to
what I say, teachers who use harassment as an
excuse to slack off, and a principal who shifts
the blame onto others.)

\N<Detective>(To top it all off, I'm even disliked by my wife
and daughter... I haven't had a proper
conversation with my daughter in years.)
\N<Detective>...I wonder how it all came to this...
\N<Detective>Sigh... Let's just finish this for now...

\N<Detective>Well... this is the end... Oh no! I missed the
last train!!
